### Official University Context:
Category: hostel application
Question: How do I apply for on-campus hostel accommodation?
Official Answer: On-campus hostel accommodation is allocated on a first-come, first-served basis, with priority given to first-year undergraduate and international students. Applications open online on the Student Portal one month before the semester starts. You must pay a non-refundable application fee first, select your preferred hostel block, and upload your proof of payment. Results are published on the portal two weeks before classes commence.

